DkAvjohug&oe=6763F357"}, {"file_name": "Back9Board_2K_PNG.png", "id": "262169482485579", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57569440_262169485818912_8878709059878914615_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2qEuQ-O_nzgQ7kNvgGW1QsB&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA49i8vB5XdPkNTk1ngVN-L6BVSYMZpxE9yUMaZ6Sm1UA&oe=67640938"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "DiscBenders_CoverArt_16-9_2K_PNG.png", "id": "610076236830296", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982512_610076240163629_3637108208520596054_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=_hvb2hAyLUMQ7kNvgHqh8_V&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAh93MJrdQYW6EqGMyFf5esAXT3UaamFUzbI2x796fxZw&oe=67640379"}, "display_name": "Disc Benders: Ace Run", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Disc Benders is the ultimate Disc Golf simulator | Hone your disc throwing skills in challenging courses and relaxing environments\n\nNow boasts four full courses, with over 45+ holes to play, five unique disc types to choose from, and two game modes: Free Play & Career Mode\n\nReview your course play at the post-game review board, with career stats that carry across play sessions, and visualizations of your throws for your round.\n\nBend alongside up to 4 of your friends (and others) as you keep score and socialize on the course.\n\nFreshly designed 9-hole course 'Dream Drop Bends' will test your ability to throw flexes and high elevation shots, with pro-level distances\n\n\n*WARNING: Game is no longer in development - Experience is a finished product*", "short_description": "Disc Benders is the ultimate Disc Golf simulator | Hone your disc throwing skills in challenging courses and relaxing environments"}]}, "developer_name": "Free Fall Studios", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://freefallstudiosgames.wixsite.com/discbenders/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_na